{
  "stem": "27507.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People had decision to face whether to move into the ghetto or whether to try to stay in the Aryan side of Warsaw, pretending that one was Polish and pretending that one was Catholic and not Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was, of course, thing which a number of very assimilated Jews did just that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They never moved into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They stayed immediately because they were as well probably further seeing than the rest of us, and they could see that it was-- it ultimately was going to end--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bad-- --very badly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for my parents, I don't think that it, even at this moment, it was an option.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think they even considered it at this moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were as well-- the, the whole family moved into the ghetto and there was simply nobody even thought about it that one could have stayed outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was obvious that one had to move into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was forced for Jews to move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one was forced, but as well, they didn't even consider the alternative of not going into the ghetto, of hiding in the Polish part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what should I talk about?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Should I talk about what to ghetto was or how it was?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, the flat was-- the flat, we still had some of the furniture from before the war, so some of the furniture and some of the furniture was gone, as I explained.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some furniture still remained and we got some of that furniture into that flat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The flat was not particularly beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was darkish in a typical Warsaw apartment block, which was mainly apartment blocks built around the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
